descriptionHtml:
[center][u][size=3]Makes Serana a preset in Racemenu

Just use Racemenu and choose Nord, switch to female and her preset should be the very last one.

[color=#ffff00]Made with base game Racemenu,[/color] but I'm sure it would work for [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?]Racemenu[/url][/size][/u] as well.
She comes with Serana's armor and Hood, which you can find by the south gate in Riverwood. (see picture)[/center]
author: UrValdBagina
